data.description: **Assumable FHA loan at 2.85% interest rate available!** Your urban farm awaits in coveted Coeur D'Alene! Welcome to this unique, updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom rancher with an open living room, kitchen and dining room. Throughout the home you'll find modern fixtures, industrial open shelving, updated bathrooms, and spacious bedrooms. The home exterior boasts a new skylight and roof with a 40-year warranty. If you are a gardening enthusiast or dream of homesteading, the thoughtfully placed raised garden beds in the front and back yard are ready for your creative gardening touches. Relax in the private backyard on the large gravel patio area and enjoy the recently re-done, low maintenance landscaping. There's a spacious parking pad for your RV or toys that makes it easy to enjoy the close access to the CDA National Forest.
